==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Lousy
<hw>Lous"y</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Infested
with lice.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Mean; contemptible; <as>as, <ex>lousy</ex>
knave</as>.</def> <mark>[informal]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Such <qex>lousy</qex> learning as this is.</q>
<rj><qau>Bale.</qau></rj></p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>Very bad; <as>as, to feel <ex>lousy</ex>; to do a
<ex>lousy</ex> job</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Lout</ent>⟦br⟧
